main event: A series of UFO sightings occurred in Holly Hill, Florida on December 6, 1966, involving multiple witnesses reporting a white object that changed colors and disappeared at high speed.
interesting points: The object was about the size of a silver dollar held at arm's length,The color of the object changed from white to red and blue, then back to white,More than one object was sighted, with reports of six in total,Two other residents corroborated the sighting, describing similar behaviors of the objects,Witnesses claimed the objects made no sound during the sighting.
sighted object: A white object that changed colors, possibly multiple objects
witness description: A group of residents, including teenagers and adults, some of whom reported seeing multiple objects.
